Fluincy helps companies uncover revenue from everyday conversations.

This extension allows users to automatically turn on the transcription feature in Google Meet. It still requires the user to ensure that everyone in the meeting is aware of the transcription and to enable it but it gets them to the accept screen without any additional interaction.
